docs/components/progress-steps-26","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#not-started","content":"Omit `currentStep` for a flow that hasn't begun: every step is `future` and none is marked current."},"739":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-27","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#vertical","content":"Use `orientation=\"vertical\"` to place the accent bar on the leading edge and stack steps in a column."},"740":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-28","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#interactive","content":"Give a step an `onPress` handler to make it navigable. Steps without `onPress` are inert."},"741":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-29","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#disabled","content":"A disabled interactive step is muted, removed from the tab order, and cannot be activated."},"742":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-30","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#hide-step-numbers","content":"Step numbers are prepended automatically. Set `hideStepNumbers` to omit them."},"743":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-31","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#customization","content":"Step numbers (`\"N. \"`) are prepended automatically — keep them where possible, as user testing shows people recognize the component better with them. Set `hideStepNumbers` to omit them."},"744":{"id":"/docs/components/progress-steps-32","page_id":"/docs/components/progress-steps","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/progress-steps#customization","content":"`orientation` switches between `horizontal` (accent bar on top) and `vertical` (accent 